title: Rare Hits of The 80's Vol. 66
description:
It's time we discovered some more fantastic music from our beloved decade, some you might have heard and some totally new to you. I gotta say, vol. 66 is the darkest of all in this installments. You know by now that I have a penchant for diversity when doing these mixes, but I gotta say on vol. 66 the focus is almost entirely on goth wave, dark wave and post-punk music. These artists and bands largely remained in obscurity, nonetheless produced some of the finest music of the 80's. I think you'd be enthralled with this one.
